{"tid":2148417,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報：港區國安法立法後續在Twitter唱衰香港　黎智英指外國或聯合對抗","createTime":"2020-08-10T02:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T02:57:45.000Z","uid":28114,"like":7,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"83c0cd715988a9b7437b68ca190a4f7956e62819","tid":2148417,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200810/bkn-20200810093730500-0810_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200810%2Fbkn-20200810093730500-0810_00822_001.html&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25YjHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=8c0a55b6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200810/bkn-20200810093730500-0810_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200810/photo/bkn-20200810093730500-0810_00822_001_01p.jpg?20200810102127\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200810%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200810093730500-0810_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20200810102127&h=9315726c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黎智英在《港區國安法》實施後仍多次在Twitter進行直播「唱衰」香港。(胡德威攝)<br />\n《港區國安法》實施超過1個月，警方國安處今早(10日)拘捕壹傳媒黎智英，涉違國安法。翻查其社交媒體，黎在港區國安法實施後，仍多次在Twitter進行直播「唱衰」香港。<br />\n<br />\n其中在上月23日，黎智英在社交網站Twitter進行直播「唱衰」香港，他公開承認現時街頭抗爭很困難，若要堅持抗爭，就需要將戰場轉移至立法會內。<br />\n<br />\n黎又聲稱，中國在當時推出國安法是一個錯誤，不少港人在國安法訂立後感到害怕，考慮移民離開香港，令香港連串抗爭行動再受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n黎隨後再「唱衰」香港，揚言香港若持續遭到中國破壞，只會顯示國安法的錯誤，並且引來更多國家聯合起來對抗中國，這將會是前所未見的情況。"},{"pid":"d037e9332b9ede66871ab069bff62f257fb498dd","tid":2148417,"uid":244346,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:29:47.000Z","msg":"so fragile<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b2cdde3ff9acfc6e5dfc9752d1ca983ffbea956","tid":2148417,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T02:30:15.000Z","msg":"唱衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 